1
00:00:07,640 --> 00:00:10,280
Brother, I think it's about time.

2
00:00:10,680 --> 00:00:12,040
Let's go up.

3
00:00:14,520 --> 00:00:15,520
Wait a bit longer.

4
00:00:36,720 --> 00:00:38,650
I don't like other men touching me.

5
00:00:49,800 --> 00:00:51,800
It's about time. Let's go.

6
00:00:52,680 --> 00:00:53,720
Let's go.

7
00:00:57,680 --> 00:00:58,480
Mr. Zhi.

8
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:00,880
Thank you for your hard work.

9
00:01:01,160 --> 00:01:02,560
This is your tuition fee.

10
00:01:06,120 --> 00:01:06,920
Who are you?

11
00:01:09,240 --> 00:01:10,560
She asked me to come.

12
00:01:11,000 --> 00:01:11,920
Who are you?

13
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,200
Are you okay?

14
00:01:28,240 --> 00:01:30,000
Lao Er, keep an eye on him.

15
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,160
No, no, no.

16
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:36,400
Aiyuan.

17
00:01:36,960 --> 00:01:37,560
I'm sorry.

18
00:02:10,720 --> 00:02:12,920
Boss, there's a phone,

19
00:02:13,200 --> 00:02:14,200
and a wallet.

20
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:17,480
That's all.

21
00:02:17,880 --> 00:02:19,920
There's another 300 on the bed.

22
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:27,880
Wife and kid.

23
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,090
With such a beautiful wife and kid,

24
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:35,220
you still come out to play around.

25
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,120
Boss,

26
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,720
we can ask his wife for money.

27
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:42,800
Don't.

28
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:45,480
I won't dare do it again. Please spare me.

29
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:51,280
Then we need something to prove he's with us.

30
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:56,980
His right hand.

31
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:01,520
Give me the knife.

32
00:03:01,920 --> 00:03:02,320
Get up.

33
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:03,600
Don't.

34
00:03:07,640 --> 00:03:09,480
He touched my woman with his right hand.

35
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,960
No, I didn't.

36
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,960
Boss.

37
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,120
From then on,

38
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:58,280
the prince and the princess lived happily ever after.

39
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,680
It must be Daddy.

40
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,680
Be a good girl and go to sleep.

41
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,079
Mommy will go take a look.

42
00:04:29,200 --> 00:04:30,120
Who are you?

43
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:32,800
How do you have the key to my house?

44
00:04:33,280 --> 00:04:34,680
You must be Yao Shufen.

45
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:37,600
Your husband asked us to deliver something to you.

46
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,880
Please come down and get it.

47
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:56,920
What did my husband ask you to bring?

48
00:05:37,280 --> 00:05:39,080
Lao Er, go up and take a look.

49
00:05:43,880 --> 00:05:46,840
Don't be nervous, Mrs. Hong.

50
00:05:46,840 --> 00:05:49,200
Let's sit down and talk.

51
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,080
What happened to my husband?

52
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,080
Is he dead?

53
00:06:49,320 --> 00:06:52,320
Don't worry, he's fine and safe right now.

54
00:06:52,880 --> 00:06:53,680
But,

55
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:57,180
do you know why I chopped off one of his hands?

56
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,159
Did he offend you?

57
00:06:59,159 --> 00:07:00,720
If he offended you,

58
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,600
can I apologize on his behalf?

59
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,610
I'm afraid you can't afford it.

60
00:07:07,120 --> 00:07:08,400
He touched my woman.

61
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,480
Boss, there's a safe inside.

62
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,480
Can't open it without the password.

63
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,080
Mrs. Hong,

64
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:20,160
what's the password?

65
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:22,280
I don't know.

66
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:24,280
You are his wife, and you don't know?

67
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,280
I really don't know.

68
00:07:25,280 --> 00:07:26,880
He never lets me touch the money.

69
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,320
I really don't know.

70
00:07:35,280 --> 00:07:36,540
Is this your daughter?

71
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,490
What's her name?

72
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,080
Nuannuan.

73
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,360
Then Nuannuan should know.

74
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:50,480
Did we find cute little Nuannuan upstairs?

75
00:07:54,360 --> 00:07:57,400
She's not here today. She's at my father's house.

76
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:58,530
What a coincidence.

77
00:07:58,760 --> 00:08:00,490
You're not lying to me, are you?

78
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,400
No.

79
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:14,140
Her daughter is indeed not upstairs.

80
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:19,560
She probably wouldn't lie to us.

81
00:08:22,160 --> 00:08:24,620
Then your husband might have to suffer a bit.

82
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:31,880
Lao San.

83
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:33,520
Ask him for the password.

84
00:08:33,520 --> 00:08:34,720
Got it. Don't worry.

85
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,360
I'm telling you,

86
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,760
I just want the password.

87
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:38,679
Don't cause any trouble.

88
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,560
You're awake.

89
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,080
Let me go.

90
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,320
I'll do anything.

91
00:09:01,680 --> 00:09:03,640
Tell me the password to your safe.

92
00:09:12,200 --> 00:09:13,280
I saw the photos.

93
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:17,400
Your wife and your daughter, choose one for me.

94
00:09:18,960 --> 00:09:20,880
If you don't choose, I'll take it as a yes.

95
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:22,160
I want both of them.

96
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:34,400
Mrs. Hong.

97
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,800
If your husband doesn't tell you,

98
00:09:36,800 --> 00:09:37,720
I will.

99
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:42,160
151902. Sorry for the trouble.

100
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,800
Lao San.

101
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:09,960
Don't spare that guy.

102
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:12,930
Wait for my call before you make a move.

103
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,520
See you at the pier after it's done.
